This is the 3rd version of cs_italiano and i hope it's the last, ive now made it (hopefully) very realistic and everything has been done to make it as visually pleasing as it could be while you add some blood to the walls =P This map is great for big and small matches and i hope you like it, at least try it and see!

feel free to contact me with any points or suggestions or a map request, ill try to do it whenever i have the time =D
